# =============================================================================
# FORGE NORA — runtime config TEMPLATE (.env.example)
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. This is a template only. The REAL file next to it is  nora.env
#   2. Copy this file:  cp nora.env.example nora.env  then edit values.
#   3. Redeploy (push.sh) so the box reloads.
#
# Nora organizes the daycare roster (new enrollments, existing kids, classroom
# capacity/ratio) and follows up on family communications (e.g. after a Family
# Text Blast, who needs a nudge). She reports to Solomon and reads his
# "family-comms" / "enrollment" delegations off the shared agent bus. She never
# takes an outward action on her own — every text/nudge stays a proposal until
# the owner taps to send it. Her only autonomous writes are her own brain
# playbook + bus notes.
#
# SAFETY:
#   This folder is a SIBLING of the web app ("forge rei/"), so it lives OUTSIDE
#   the web-served dir. Nothing here is reachable over HTTP. Keys stay private.
# =============================================================================

# --- Cadence -----------------------------------------------------------------
# Hours between Nora's autonomous roster/follow-up briefs on the box.
FORGE_NORA_BRIEF_EVERY_H=6

# --- Self-improvement --------------------------------------------------------
# Briefs Nora must produce before an auto self-improve fires.
FORGE_NORA_LEARN_EVERY=8
# Minimum minutes between self-improvement writes (rate guard).
FORGE_NORA_LEARN_GAP_MIN=45

# --- Anthropic (Nora's OWN Claude key) ---------------------------------------
# Optional. Nora's dedicated key. If unset she FALLS BACK to Solomon's key,
# then the shared agency/wholesale Anthropic key, so she works before her own
# key is set.
# NORA_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Obsidian brain (vault) --------------------------------------------------
# Optional override for the Agentic-OS Obsidian vault path. Nora reads her
# learned playbook from <vault>/Skills/nora-playbook.md in addition to the
# local skills/nora-playbook.md in this folder.
# FORGE_VAULT=/Users/yg4st/Desktop/Agentic-OS/vault
